---
title: Harissa Honey Veggie Koftas  with Greek Style Cheese Seasoned Chips and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Come rain or shine, it's time for a great British BBQ! Our summery dishes such as these Harissa Honey Veggie Koftas are designed with full-on flavour in mind. Whether you enjoy it al fresco or bring some sunshine indoors, they're perfect for BBQ season.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R21_W27_UK_V22404-3_Main_high-6d387490.jpg
